gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 112, Trail Blazers 103
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Trail Blazers 112-103. Nikola Jokic recorded 29 points, eight rebounds, and seven assists for the Nuggets, with Jamal Murray adding 21 points and 10 assists in the victory. Deandre Ayton tallied a season-high 27 points, along with nine rebounds and four assists for the Trail Blazers in the losing effort. The Nuggets improve to 35-16, while the Trail Blazers fall to 15-35.
